OL,6,FA burglar who burst into the bedroom
OL,7,Fof his victim and threw a TV at his
OL,8,Fhead has been jailed for more than
OL,9,Fseven years.
OL,11,FThe victim was at his home in
OL,12,FDanesmoor, just south of Chesterfield,
OL,13,Fin the early hours of Saturday 25
OL,14,FOctober last year when he heard loud
OL,15,Fbanging.
OL,17,FHe opened the door of his bedroom and
OL,18,Fthree men wearing face coverings burst
OL,19,Fin and pushed him backwards.
