OL,3,CMasked gang burst into bedroom and
OL,4,Cthrew TV at Chesterfield homeowner
OL,6,FThey assaulted him and one of them
OL,7,Fpulled a TV off a wall before throwing
OL,8,Fit at the homeowner's head.
OL,10,FThe men stole his wallet and mobile
OL,11,Fphone ` but the device was later
OL,12,Frecovered.
OL,14,FThe victim, a man aged in his 20s, was
OL,15,Fleft with head and arm injuries.
OL,17,FOne of the burglars was known to the
OL,18,Fvictim and later identified as Sandy
OL,19,FHughes.
