OL,6,FHughes was arrested by officers and
OL,7,Fbrought in for questioning but gave a
OL,8,Fno comment interview.
OL,10,FThe 47-year-old, of Penncroft Lane in
OL,11,FDanesmoor, was charged with aggravated
OL,12,Fburglary.
OL,14,FHe pleaded guilty to the offence and
OL,15,Fwas jailed for seven years and six
OL,16,Fmonths during a sentencing hearing at
OL,17,FDerby Crown Court on Friday 30 January.
OL,19,FHughes was also imposed with a
OL,20,Frestraining order not to contact the
OL,21,Fvictim.
