OL,6,FDetective Constable Lindsay Clarke
OL,7,Fsaid: "This was a terrifying attack in
OL,8,Fwhich Hughes invaded the property of
OL,9,Fthe victim ` a place where he should
OL,10,Fhave felt most safe ` before attacking
OL,11,Fhim and stealing his belongings.
OL,13,F"I would like to pay tribute to the
OL,14,Fvictim in this case for the co-
OL,15,Foperation and bravery they have shown
OL,16,Fin coming forward to assist the
OL,17,Finvestigation team in bringing Hughes
OL,18,Fto justice."
